{
 "file": "_STGSP5A.bin",
 "source_size": 35236,
 "built_size": 37071,
 "edits": [
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1441",
   "jp_len": 114,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "あいうえおかダチッツテ{01}デ、トドナ。ニネハバパ·々ビたプベブマミだムメっ？！ちャラリン下がつてとなぬ開我官』のはば間機貴近軍見向ま行むすじー…ね国士佐みそやょよへ死·{00}！官{00}M匂従な、{00}{01}！ゃ{00}M士1な、{00}{01}ぁ布莱德舰长！！",
   "zh_hex": "15161718191a1b6566676869016a026b6c6d036e6f7071720407732a767775797a2b7b7c2d05062c7e808185891c2e2f3133358d8b8f0d37383991929496989a9d3d9f3f2524080936a1a5a33e284344453ba70400068f0013940e33020001064200133c0d3302000115e831e846e82ce7d4ef34ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x14ce",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这边不用担心！托比亚、{00}你去拦截敌部队！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e899e7b5d8e9fde82d06e7f4e825e7d60200e7b8e7ebeb89ee27e7e3cce7c9060600000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1503",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x152e",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "各舰、立刻进入战斗态势！！把木星帝国{00}击退！",
   "zh_hex": "15e819e7d402e86be91fe892e891ef28e7ffe994e8fdef97ef97e81befa9ef69e8f8efc400e7cce880ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1576",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "150e3302000215e7c309090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x159d",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "贝拉·罗纳！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e857e7c2ef4be7ece882ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15c9",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "150e3302000215e963e85ae82a0909e963e85ae82ae7e2e955e837e7b9e7da09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15e2",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我……当初什么都不做就好了……",
   "zh_hex": "15efcc0909ef53eb4fe7dde7bde840e7b5e81ce7c5e7c7e7ba09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1613",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "贝拉·罗纳！振作起来！！你这副样子怎{00}么行！",
   "zh_hex": "15e857e7c204e7ece88206eb5bef2fe847d90606e7b8e7b9ecb6e7dae886e7f200e7bd9f06000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1653",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "150e3302000215e7c402e7c4e7b602efcc0909e840ea07efcceae7e847e7bae7b9e876ef28e8520009090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1674",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "他……金凯度他……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e80c0909e902e95fe96de80c0909ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16aa",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不是这样的、贝拉！！金凯度先生并没有{00}死！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5e7b6e7b9e7dae7b402e857e7c20606e902e95fe96db8b6e957e7d8e7cb00a7060000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16c6",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "他那种人、绝不会轻易死的！！我相信、{00}他一定还活着！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e80ce7b7e7d1efb202e91ce7b5e7e2e990e964ef6ae7b4ef97ef97efcce8b1e90f0200e80cefb6e867e7f7e8d4e86def97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x170d",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "150e3302000215e7f4e825e7d609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x173f",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "贝拉·罗纳、你还打算在悲伤里沉溺到什{00}么时候？",
   "zh_hex": "15e857e7c2ef4be7ece88202e7b8e7f7e7f5e889ef29e9dfe8f9ef31e983ee58e7d7e7dd00e7bdef2dea39050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17a2",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你可是自己选择了当指挥官的",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7c4e7b6efb5e8c9e966eaaae7baef53e8c0e949ef92e7b40000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17b7",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "如果你在这里抛下一切、辜负的就不只是{00}金凯度……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f0e871e7b8ef29e7b9ef31eaa9ef4defb6ef3f02ed0de92ce7b4e7c5e7b5ef32e7b600e902e95fe96d09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17d0",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你将会背弃所有、依然信任着你的人",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e84ae7e2e9e4e938e7fbe7cb02eafce7efe90fe89ae86de7b8e7b4efb20000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1811",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "150e3302000215e831e846e82ce7d4ef3409090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x183b",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "来吧、由你来指挥先锋母舰、贝拉·罗{00}纳！！",
   "zh_hex": "15d9e7d002e8a6e7b8d9e8c0e949b8e967e9d5e7d402e857e7c204e7ec00e882060600000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1876",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "150e3302000215efcc02efcc09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18a0",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我来做！我来！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efccefcfe81cef97efccefcfef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18d0",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "敌部队的反应、已经完全消失！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e3ef70e7c9e7b4e87ce87302ef3ae8b7e87eefb4e928e8a5ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1904",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "各舰修理完毕",
   "zh_hex": "15e819e7d4e9b0e872e87eea2c0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x192f",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……嗯",
   "zh_hex": "150909e865000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1937",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "虽然耽搁了不少时间、但这下、总算能回{00}地球了",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b8e7efeda7ed6ae7bae7b5efacef2de8fc02e7dbe7b9ef4d02e881e889e7c6ef5200ef63efd3e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1977",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "木星帝国、已经把那么庞大的一支部队、{00}送进了地球圈……",
   "zh_hex": "15efa9ef69e8f8efc402ef3ae8b7e81be7b7e7bded55efa5e7b4efb6e883ef70e7c90200e9bae892e7baef63efd3e9fb09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1998",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "他们露出獠牙、恐怕已经只是时间问题了",
   "zh_hex": "15e80ce7bbe858efbeececebd702eb33e958ef3ae8b7ef32e7b6ef2de8fce997ea12e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19cf",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "拦得住吗？……单凭我们的力量",
   "zh_hex": "15eb89e80ae859e802050909e918ea498be7bbe7b4dae85100000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19fb",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……不",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b50000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a02",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "单靠我们隆德·贝尔来应对、事态实在太{00}严重了",
   "zh_hex": "15e918e8c7efcce7bbed16e82cef4be857e7e1efcfe873e7be02efb8e994e87fef29e86a00eaa1e8a1e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a1f",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "联系军本部求援",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ee941e7e0efa6ef70e93ae8630000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a4b",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "如果木星帝国的目标是地球、那便片刻也{00}不能耽搁了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f0e871efa9ef69e8f8efc4e7b4efd4e96fe7b6ef63efd302e7b7e8faee5ee91fe7c000e7b5e7c6eda7ed6ae7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a6d",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "必须尽快与正规军会合、做好迎击入侵的{00}准备才行",
   "zh_hex": "15e860e9a2e8f2e85fe832ef3bea42e7e0e7e2efc002e81ce7c7e931e7cce891ea46e7b400e87ae877e836efd60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1aac",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "各舰立即出发！",
   "zh_hex": "15e819e7d4e86be855efbee870ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1abd",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "托雷斯、立刻联络军本部！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f4e8afe7c802e86be91fef2eeb14e7e0d2cc060000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1aca",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "与正规军会合之后、全力阻止木星帝国军{00}的进攻！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e832ef3bea42e7e0e7e2efc0e7cde7fe02efb4efb0e8efe869efa9ef69e8f8efc4e7e000e7b4e892ef67ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x60d2",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……不好！这艘舰要是被打沉……！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b5e7c7ef97e7b9eb18e7d4ef2ae7b6e7f1e7f5e9830909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x629a",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呵呵呵……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3def3def3d09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x62ca",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你就是十字先锋的扎比涅·夏尔吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7c5e7b6ea4ae980b8e967e7b4e84be825eacf04ef37e7e1e7d00500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x62de",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……联络、我已经收到了",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef2eeb1402efccef3ae8b7e926e7d7e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x631e",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、投降的条件也……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e948e943e7b4e9d4e991e7c009090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6351",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我会保证你、以及贝拉·罗纳舰长的安全",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7e2ea47eba3e7b802e7f3e9cfe857e7c2ef4be7ece882e7d4ef34e7b4e7fcefb40000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6382",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶！就没别的办法了吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7deef97e7c5e7d8e7e5e7b4e8eae84ee7bae802ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x63b0",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "先锋母舰上、可是有布莱特舰长在啊！",
   "zh_hex": "15b8e967e9d5e7d4b202e7c4e7b6e7cbe831e846e7cfe7d4ef34ef29e7c30600000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x63c4",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "要是轻举妄动的话……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ae7b6e990ea21ecc6ef30e7b4e81f09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x63fa",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……没错、你们最好别轻举妄动",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7d8e88502e7b8e7bbe8c5e7c7e7e5e990ea21ecc6ef300000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x640c",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "先锋母舰的主炮、可正对准着你们呢",
   "zh_hex": "15b8e967e9d5e7d4e7b4e954e95a02e7c4ef3be7bee87ae86de7b8e7bbe9070000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6424",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "敢乱动……呵呵",
   "zh_hex": "15e8cde976ef300909ef3def3d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x645a",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81def97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6497",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "扎比涅！你这家伙！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e84be825eacf06e7b8e7b9e7dfe7fd06060000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x64b8",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啧！是金凯度吗！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e9faef97e7b6e902e95fe96de802ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x64ea",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶！是海盗的同伙吗！！全员、进入战{00}斗配置……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7deef97e7b6e91be9f3e7b4e85de7fde802ef97ef97efb4e84902e892e891ef2800e7ffea34ea0e09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6538",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……等等！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e826e826ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6566",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81def97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x659e",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "放走他、是我的疏忽……那就由我负责、{00}亲手了结他",
   "zh_hex": "15e86ce890e80c02e7b68be7b4ee6eed770909e7b7e7c5e8a68be92ceba60200e894aee7bae868e80c0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x65df",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……好、好吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909e7c702e7c7e7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6612",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……就是这么回事、金凯度",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c5e7b6e7b9e7bdef52efb802e902e95fe96d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6620",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我不想让旁人插手、和你单独做个了断、{00}嘿嘿……",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b5e7e6e7f9ef04efb2eb08ef6602e7d3e7b8e918e8eee81ce828e7bae9820200e85ee85e09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6670",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "扎比涅、你想干什么？",
   "zh_hex": "15e84be825eacf02e7b8e7e6e8d3e7dde7bd050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x669e",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……来吧、放马过来、金凯度",
   "zh_hex": "150909efcfe7d002e86ce84fef36efcf02e902e95fe96d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x66ad",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你若能打倒我、我答应放了贝拉大人、又{00}何妨？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7e7e7c6e7f5e848efcc02efccea96e873e86ce7bae857e7c2efa5efb202e8f100efbce97f050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x66cd",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哈、哈哈、哈！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e802e7e8e7e802e7e8ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x670b",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啧、扎比涅……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e9fa02e84be825eacf090906000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x674b",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……好吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c7e7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6755",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你的算计……我就奉陪到底！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b4e889ea550909efcce7c5eac1ef42e7d7e9b4ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x677c",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哈、哈哈哈！！这才像样、金凯度！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e802e7e8e7e8e7e8ef97ef97e7b9e836e8e9e7da02e902e95fe96def97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x67ae",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呵呵呵、我就知道你会上当",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3def3def3d028be7c5e85ae82ae7b8e7e2b2c40000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6821",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "毕竟、你和我之间……",
   "zh_hex": "15ea2cef2c02e7b8e7d3efcce7cde8fc09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6830",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "看来、你我之间、注定要决一死战啊！{00}金凯度——！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f6d902e7b88be7cde8fc02eacce867ef2ae8ab87a7ef28e7c30600e902e95fe96debafebaf060600000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6887",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "打倒你、把贝拉救出来……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f5e848e7b802e81be857e7c2e8caefbeefcf09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6899",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……做好觉悟吧！扎比涅——！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e81ce7c7e8aeea19e7d006e84be825eacfebafebaf06060000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x68d2",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……啧！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e9faef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6902",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "到此为止了！扎比涅！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d7e7cae7c1e869e7ba06e84be825eacf06060000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6936",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嘿嘿嘿嘿！当真如此吗、金凯度——！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e85ee85ee85ee85eef97ef53e820e7f0e7cae80202e902e95fe96debafebafef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6976",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么、你这家伙！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bd02e7b8e7b9e7dfe7fdef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x699a",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶！竟没能给他致命一击吗！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7deef97ef2ce7d8e7c6e839e80cea32e853efb6e7cce802ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x69e2",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "金凯度……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e902e95fe96d0909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x69f4",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "只要、只要没有你这个人……！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef32ef2a02ef32ef2ae7d8e7cbe7b8e7b9e828efb20909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6a12",
   "jp_len": 40,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "贝拉大人若不是对你动了心、又怎会舍弃{00}贵族主义！",
   "zh_hex": "15e857e7c2efa5efb2e7e7e7b5e7b6e7bee7b8ef30e7bae82d02e8f1e7f2e7e2eb17e93800e930eb5ee954e8ceef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6a6a",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "拿命来赎罪吧！！金凯度！",
   "zh_hex": "15e9a7e853efcfeff1ea7fe7d0ef97ef97e902e95fe96def970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6aae",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "糟了！？",
   "zh_hex": "15eeafe7ba06050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6ae6",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "金凯度！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e902e95fe96def97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6b12",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "贝、贝拉……对不起……",
   "zh_hex": "15e85702e857e7c20909e7bee7b5e84709090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6b4e",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊哈哈哈！啊哈哈哈哈哈！！永别了！金{00}凯度！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c3e7e8e7e8e7e8ef97e7c3e7e8e7e8e7e8e7e8e7e8ef97ef97e9bfe7e5e7baef97e90200e95fe96def970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6b96",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "金凯度——！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e902e95fe96debafebafef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6bc9",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "150e3302000215e7c4e7deef97e902e95fe96def8bef8de80cef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6c00",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "150e3302000215e7f4e825e7d60909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6c30",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "150e3302000215ef8be967efade884e833e7f1ea1702e7b9ef4de86ee902e95fe96def8bef8de7c0090009ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6c4e",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……可恶！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c4e7deef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6c87",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "150e3302000215e7c302e7f4e825e7d6ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6cd2",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……是托比亚吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909e7b6e7f4e825e7d6e8020605000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6cf8",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你们这帮家伙……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7bbe7b9e910e7dfe7fd0909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6d0d",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "别给我开这种玩笑啊——！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e5e839efcce7fae7b9e7d1e970ea1ce7c3ebafebafef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6d4a",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……就趁现在！让先锋母舰后撤！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c5e9eae82fef2906e7f9b8e967e9d5e7d4e7fee90a06060000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6d91",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "150e3302000215e7c30909efcc02efcc0909e902e95fe96de80c09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6dc4",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "让舰后退、贝拉·罗纳！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f9e7d4e7fee88002e857e7c2ef4be7ece882ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6dfa",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "script",
   "zh_hex": "150e3302000215e7c309090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6e06",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "先、先锋母舰……全速后撤……",
   "zh_hex": "15b802b8e967e9d5e7d40909bbe9dae7fee90a090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6e3a",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啧！是海盗！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e9faef97e7b6e91be9f3ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6e6e",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "先锋母舰！全舰、转入攻击态势！！",
   "zh_hex": "15b8e967e9d5e7d406bbe7d402e9c2e8919ee7cce994e8fd060600000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6e7f",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "把木星帝国军、彻底击破！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81befa9ef69e8f8efc4e7e002ebc5e9b4e7ccef6def97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6eb6",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好！其余各舰、也跟上先锋母舰！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c706e8cfeb27e819e7d402e7c0e973b2b8e967e9d5e7d40606000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6ec9",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "隆德·贝尔队！从现在起、转入反击！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ed16e82cef4be857e7e1e7c9ef97e88ae82fef29e84702e9c2e891e87ce7ccef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6f06",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "看来你已经重新振作起来了、贝拉·罗纳",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f6efcfe7b8ef3ae8b7e8a1ef8aeb5bef2fe847efcfe7ba02e857e7c2ef4be7ece8820000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6f36",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6f3d",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "只顾悲伤、会辜负那人的付出",
   "zh_hex": "15ef32ea1fe9dfe8f902e7e2ed0de92ce7b7efb2e7b4e97eefbe0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6f5d",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "胸口的这份痛、虽然无法抹去……但我们{00}绝不能就此止步",
   "zh_hex": "15ee8ceabde7b4e7b9ea22ea0b02e8b8e7efe7dce84eecd9e7eb0909e7db8be7bb00e91ce7b5e7c6e7c5e7cae869ea93000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6f82",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "所以、我……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7fbe7f302efcc09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6fb2",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔、又来了新的敌军……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d02e8f1efcfe7baef8ae7b4e7e3e7e00909ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6fe6",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……布莱特舰长！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e831e846e7cfe7d4ef3406000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x700b",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不妙、经过刚才那一战、我们的战力已大{00}不如前……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ecc702e8b7ef36e8bce836e7b7efb6ef2802efcce7bbe7b4ef28efb0ef3aefa500e7b5e7f0ef5109090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x704e",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "全舰、准备攻击！",
   "zh_hex": "15efb4e7d402e87ae877ef67e7ccef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7059",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "向违抗杜加奇总统的海盗们、降下制裁的{00}铁锤吧！",
   "zh_hex": "159deab2e912e8cbe854e904e881e929e7b4e91be9f3e7bb02e94389e8deec39e7b400eebbedc2e7d0060000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x709e",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "等等！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e826e826ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x70ce",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "贝尔纳黛特！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e857e7e1e882ea9ae7cfef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x70fe",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不许你们、对这些人动手！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5e8a7e7b8e7bb02e7bee7b9e8a4efb2ef30ef66ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7130",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什、什么、你是谁！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dd02e7dde7bd02e7b8e7b6e923ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7159",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我、是提提妮斯·杜加奇",
   "zh_hex": "158b02e7b6e821e821ebbce7c804e8cbe854e90400000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7163",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是格拉克斯·杜加奇总统的女儿",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e824e7c2e7d5e7c804e8cbe854e904e881e929e7b4b0eb7c00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x718d",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎、怎么会……贝尔纳黛特？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f202e7f2e7bde7e20909e857e7e1e882ea9ae7cf050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x71b6",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那孩子、竟是杜加奇的……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e956e88602ef2ce7b6e8cbe854e904e7b40909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x71ea",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "司、司令……那张脸、的确是提提妮斯大{00}人的……",
   "zh_hex": "15eafe02eafee94e0909e7b7eac5eb6902e7b4e88ce7b6e821e821ebbce7c8efa500efb2e7b409090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x721f",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔、唔唔……",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d02e81de81d09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7252",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "父亲杜加奇、此刻一定正在四处找我……",
   "zh_hex": "15e888e894e8cbe854e90402e7cae91f87e867ef3bef29eb52e903e9d28b090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x726b",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "只要你们肯放过他们、我就跟你们一起、{00}回到父亲身边",
   "zh_hex": "15ef32ef2ae7b8e7bbe93de86cef36e80ce7bb02efcce7c5e973e7b8e7bbefb6e8470200ef52e7d7e888e894e88de8990000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x72aa",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那……是真的吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b70909e7b6e820e7b4e802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x72d1",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "身为总统的女儿、我绝不食言",
   "zh_hex": "15e88de7c1e881e929e7b4efadeb7c02efcce91ce7b5edc9efd70000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7308",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那好吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7c7e7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7314",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、作为接您回去的交换、就放过那些{00}人吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02ef2fe7c1efcee835ef52e7ebe7b4e861ea7802e7c5e86cef36e7b7e8a400efb2e7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x735a",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……司令！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909eafee94eef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x737e",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "无妨！提提妮斯大人的安危才是首要！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dce97fef97e821e821ebbce7c8efa5efb2e7b4e7fce935e836e7b6ef40ef2aef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x73b1",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7b609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x73d3",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "终归是支垂死的部队、放着不管、也成不{00}了什么气候",
   "zh_hex": "15e8e2e947e7b6e883ed41ef6ae7b4ef70e7c902e86ce86de7b5e93b02e7c0e837e7b500e7bae7dde7bde8edea390000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x73f3",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "再说、就算我们不特意出手、反正他们也{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15e80be7ed02e7c5e889efcce7bbe7b5e7cfef3cefbeef6602e87cef3be80ce7bbe7c00009090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x744f",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "快、护送提提妮斯大人回去！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e85f02e8e0e9bae821e821ebbce7c8efa5efb2ef52e7ebef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7486",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……贝尔纳黛特！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e857e7e1e882ea9ae7cfef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x74ac",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "别担心、托比亚",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e5e9fde82d02e7f4e825e7d60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x74b8",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我、会去见父亲大人、试着说服他停止这{00}场战争",
   "zh_hex": "15efcc02e7e2e7ebe85ce888e894efa5efb202e91de86de7ede9f1e80ce934e869e7b900e876ef28e8520000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x74f1",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请吧……提提妮斯大人",
   "zh_hex": "15e83ae7d00909e821e821ebbce7c8efa5efb20000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7516",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7542",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶……贝尔纳黛特！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7de0909e857e7e1e882ea9ae7cfef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x759a",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……贝拉",
   "zh_hex": "150909e857e7c20000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x75be",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊……托比亚？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c30909e7f4e825e7d6050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x75e2",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那个……金凯度先生的事……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e8280909e902e95fe96def8bef8de7b4efb809090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x760c",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你在为我担心吗？谢谢你、托比亚",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8ef29e7c18be9fde82de80205e8b2e8b2e7b802e7f4e825e7d6000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x761f",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过、我没事的",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef3602efcce7d8efb8e7b40000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7630",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你也一直担心着她、我也不能光顾着伤心{00}啊",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7c0efb6e875e9fde82de86de88e02efcce7c0e7b5e7c6e83dea1fe86de8f9e82d00e7c30000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7670",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "金、金凯度先生他！金凯度先生他还没有{00}死！",
   "zh_hex": "15e90202e902e95fe96def8bef8de80cef97e902e95fe96def8bef8de80ce7f7e7d8e7cb00ef6aef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x768a",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就凭那点事、他怎么可能会死啊！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5ea49e7b7e822efb802e80ce7f2e7bde7c4e7c6e7e2ef6ae7c3ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x76c1",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……没关系的、托比亚",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7d8e8bbe941e7b402e7f4e825e7d60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x76cd",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "人啊、不管怎样、该走的时候……终究还{00}是会走的",
   "zh_hex": "15efb2e7c302e7b5e93be7f2e7da02e898e890e7b4ef2dea390909e8e2e906e7f700e7b6e7e2e890e7b40000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7726",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "从前啊……",
   "zh_hex": "15e88aef51e7c309090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7749",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "贝拉……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e857e7c20909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x776e",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在我下定决心要与木星帝国一战的那一天{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29efccef4de867e8abe82def2ae832efa9ef69e8f8efc4efb6ef28e7b4e7b7efb6e8440009090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7788",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那个人、舍弃了过去的名字、选择以金凯{00}度自称",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e828efb202eb17e938e7baef36e7ebe7b4e8ace98002e966eaaae7f3e902e95f00e96defb5ea010000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x77c1",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "过去的名字……他舍弃了西布克·阿诺这{00}个名字……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef36e7ebe7b4e8ace9800909e80ceb17e938e7bae7f8e831e7d5ef4be7d2e972e7b900e828e8ace98009090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x77f7",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……嗯",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8650000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x77fe",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我不明白那究竟是为什么、就算去问他、{00}他也始终不肯回答",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b5ef39e809e7b7e906ef2ce7b6e7c1e7dde7bd02e7c5e889e7ebe997e80c0200e80ce7c0e908e8e2e7b5e93def52ea960000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7820",
   "jp_len": 40,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "因为他总是陪在我身边……我便自以为、{00}彼此的心意早已相通",
   "zh_hex": "15ef33e7c1e80ce881e7b6ef42ef29efcce88de8990909efcce8faefb5e7f3e7c10200efc9e7cae7b4e82def3ce963ef3ae8b1ef590000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7848",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "所以、我没有再追问下去",
   "zh_hex": "15e7fbe7f3028be7d8e7cbe80be8dde99789e7eb000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x785b",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "但说不定那时起……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dbe7ede7b5e867e7b7ef2de84709090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x786e",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "也许、我并没有像自己以为的那样、真正{00}读懂他的心",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c0e8a702efcce957e7d8e7cbe8e9efb5e8c9e7f3e7c1e7b4e7b7e7da02e820ef3b00eea0e8b0e80ce7b4e82d0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x78ad",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是这样吗",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6e7b9e7dae8020000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x78d4",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "咦……？",
   "zh_hex": "15ef490909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x78f6",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "贝拉以前、不也叫塞西莉·菲亚查德吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e857e7c2e7f3ef5102e7b5e7c0e8c1e950e7f8e81eef4bea6ce7d6eae9e82ce802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7934",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嗯、嗯……那是为了躲开身为贵族主义者{00}的祖父……",
   "zh_hex": "15e86502e8650909e7b7e7b6e7c1e7baea6fe7fae88de7c1e930eb5ee954e8ceef6e00e7b4ebe1e88809090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x796f",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可是、金凯度先生……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7b602e902e95fe96def8bef8d09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x797b",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不、对西布克·阿诺来说、那才是他真正{00}的名字",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b502e7bee7f8e831e7d5ef4be7d2e972efcfe7ed02e7b7e836e7b6e80ce820ef3b00e7b4e8ace9800000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x79b1",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我的、真名……",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b402e820e8ac09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x79d9",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "金凯度·纳乌这个名字、",
   "zh_hex": "15e902e95fe96def4be882e94de7b9e828e8ace980020000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x79e8",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是为了陪伴想要再次扮演贝拉·罗纳的你{00}才需要的",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e7c1e7baef42ea72e7e6ef2ae80be864ec70ea2fe857e7c204e7ece882e7b4e7b800e836e92def2ae7b40000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7a09",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是他所扮演角色的名字……我有这样的{00}感觉",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e80ce7fbec70ea2feb1ae89fe7b4e8ace98009098be7cbe7b9e7dae7b400e87de8ae000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7a68",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……啊、我说话太放肆了、真对不起",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c302efcce7ede81fe86ae86cedaae7ba02e820e7bee7b5e8470000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7a9a",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不……谢谢你、托比亚",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b50909e8b2e8b2e7b802e7f4e825e7d60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7af5",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "（金凯度先生……他之所以需要一个扮演{00}的名字……）",
   "zh_hex": "15ef8ee902e95fe96def8bef8d0909e80ce7cde7fbe7f3e92def2aefb6e828ec70ea2f00e7b4e8ace9800909ef8f0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7b11",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "（不正是为了、在战斗结束之后、变回真{00}正的两个人吗？）",
   "zh_hex": "15ef8ee7b5ef3be7b6e7c1e7ba02ef29ef28e7ffe868e895e7cde7fe02e955ef52e82000ef3be7b4e97de828efb2e80205ef8f0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7b34",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "（可是、一切都还没有结束）",
   "zh_hex": "15ef8ee7c4e7b602efb6ef3fe840e7f7e7d8e7cbe868e895ef8f0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7b48",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "（所以、金凯度先生……）",
   "zh_hex": "15ef8ee7fbe7f302e902e95fe96def8bef8d0909ef8f0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7b56",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "（你、是一定要回来的）",
   "zh_hex": "15ef8ee7b802e7b6efb6e867ef2aef52efcfe7b4ef8f0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7b6a",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "（回到这里……回到贝拉身边……）",
   "zh_hex": "15ef8eef52e7d7e7b9ef310909ef52e7d7e857e7c2e88de8990909ef8f0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7b9a",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你回来了……提提妮斯",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8ef52efcfe7ba0909e821e821ebbce7c80000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7bc3",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "父、父亲大人……",
   "zh_hex": "15e88802e888e894efa5efb209090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7bea",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "久违的父女相见、就让我听听、你想说些{00}什么吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e9dbeab2e7b4e888efade8b1e85c02e7c5e7f9efcce8d1e8d102e7b8e7e6e7ede8a400e7dde7bde7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7c0d",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "提提妮斯、你想向我杜加奇求取什么？是{00}自由吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e821e821ebbce7c802e7b8e7e69d8be8cbe854e904e93ae987e7dde7bd05e7b600abe8a6e802050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7c3d",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我、我希望您、能停止对地球的进攻……",
   "zh_hex": "15efcc02efcce87be965e83502e7c6e934e869e7beef63efd3e7b4e892ef6709090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7c75",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哦？",
   "zh_hex": "15e919050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7c96",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "即便那是为了、给木星的人民、带来一片{00}富饶的土地……",
   "zh_hex": "15e855e8fae7b7e7b6e7c1e7ba02e839d4b5e7b4b4ef3802e937d987ee5e00ec8feab5e7b4ec56bf09090000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7cbc",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我、我也绝不认为、那是正确的事！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcc02efcce7c0e91ce7b5e8a0e7c102e7b7e7b6ef3be88ce7b4efb8ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7cd8",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "所以、父亲大人……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7fbe7f302e888e894efa5efb209090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7d00",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呵……呵……！哈哈哈哈哈哈！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3d0909ef3d0909ef97e7e8e7e8e7e8e7e8e7e8e7e8ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7d14",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "进攻地球！你说进攻地球！？真是笑死人{00}了！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e892ef67ef63efd3ef97e7b8e7ede892ef67ef63efd3ef9705e820e7b6ea1cef6aefb200e7baef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7d4c",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "父、父亲大人……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e88802e888e894efa5efb20909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7d74",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "提提妮斯、你此刻呼吸着的这空气、是什{00}么？",
   "zh_hex": "15e821e821ebbce7c802e7b8e7cae91fea3ced34e86de7b4e7b9e93fe8ed02e7b6e7dd00e7bd050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7da6",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……诶？",
   "zh_hex": "150909eaf3050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7dc8",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你平时喝的那些水、又是从哪来的！给我{00}好好想想！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e887ef2dec54e7b4e7b7e8a4ebd402e8f1e7b6e88ae8ffefcfe7b4ef97e839efcc00e7c7e7c7e7e6e7e6ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7e2c",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么都没有！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bde840e7d8e7cbef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7e37",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在木星上！根本没有任何、从地球带来的{00}东西！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29efa9ef69ef4cef97e9b8efa6e7d8e7cbe89aefbc02e88aef63efd3e937efcfe7b400e8bae7f8ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7e50",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "没错……一切、都能靠人工来供给！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d8e8850909efb6ef3f02e840e7c6e8c7efb2eae4efcfeca9e839ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7e66",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7e6e",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就算把地球弄到手、又能有多大的意义？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5e889e81bef63efd3eac4e7d7ef6602e8f1e7c6e7cbe7e9efa5e7b4ef3ce8ce050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7ea1",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "父、父亲大人……{00}您到底、想做什么……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e88802e888e894beb4090900e835e7d7e9b402e7e6e81ce7dde7bd09090500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7ed7",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……哼",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8b30000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7ede",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我要的、是对全人类的支配……",
   "zh_hex": "15efccef2ae7b402e7b6e7beefb4efb2e841e7b4e883ea3409090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7ee9",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我不需要地球！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b5e92def2aef63efd3ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7f15",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8982",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊啊！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c3e7c3ef97050000"
  }
 ]
}
